Show description:
Comedian Rick Mercer invites a bevy of Canadian political heads to his satire-filled program. His poignant, smart and snappy approach makes them come to life, no matter how boring they appear. The host also takes to the road, visiting communities across Canada to see what people on the street are thinking about current affairs.



Complete Season 12, which aired from October 2014 - March 2015
